text.paragraph:
Lidocaine Ointment USP, 5% contains a local anesthetic agent and is administered topically. See 
                        INDICATIONS AND USAGE
                      for specific uses. Lidocaine Ointment USP, 5% contains lidocaine, which is chemically designated as acetamide, 2-(diethylamino)-N-(2,6-dimethylphenyl)-, and has the following structural formula:
